<AnimatedNumber value={42} duration={1000} />  // faster
How it works: runs a setInterval every 16ms (~60fps), increments by target/frames each tick, clears itself when it hits the target. The return () => clearInterval(timer) cleanup prevents memory leaks if the component unmounts mid-animation.

