### How it all connects
```
useInView()          → fires once when element enters viewport
useAnimatedProgress() → smoothly goes 0→1 using requestAnimationFrame + easeOut
progress × fullSize  → apply to height / strokeDashoffset / strokeDasharray
The single progress value (0 to 1) drives everything — multiply it against whatever dimension you want to animate. No library needed.
